jobListings.description:
Graduate of a university Psychology department;

Sees themselves as competent to work with special needs individuals;

Preferably has received Play therapy / Floortime training,

Has completed or is pursuing a master's degree in Clinical Psychology/Developmental Psychology;

Resides in the districts of Kartepe, İzmit, or Derince with no transportation issues,

We are looking for a disciplined, positive, cheerful, patient team member who communicates well with children!
